title: The Dead Linger Build 14a + Multiplayer
description:
Description:

 The Dead Linger is the definitive zombie apocalypse survival horror experience! Set in a planet-sized, procedurally generated world, survivors learn to fight, run, and survive against the never-ending and relentless zombie hordes. With pure sandbox, free-roam gameplay, multiplayer, exploration, barricading, physics, and intense realism, this is the zombie apocalypse experience you've longed for all these years. The zombie genre has died. We're bringing it back from the dead.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Installation: 

1. Extract The RAR File

2. Play!


NOTE: The Game takes awhile to load when you boot it up, so don't panic when you're waiting for it to load while staring at the black screen.

NOTE2: Be sure to change your ingame name in the lumaemu file to whatever you want.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

If you enjoy the game Buy It!! The devs are really cool! 


Remember to seed! Seeding means you're really awesome and stuff! :D
